summary: The more I think about that picture of Harry Nick posted on his Instagram story the more soft I get. Like you know Harry told...
body:
The more I think about that picture of Harry Nick posted on his Instagram story the more soft I get. Like you know Harry told Nick to post it - absolutely he did otherwise we’d never have seen it. Nick so rarely posts anything to do with Harry too which got me wondering why we were graced with this lovely image. And to me it seems like that was Harry’s way of letting people know he was there for Nick during his last week of Breakfast even if he wasn’t an actual guest.

He’s always there for Nick, no matter what, just like Nick is always there for him and that ruins me in the best way.
